Class Newton

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Newton

  • public final class Newton
extends java.lang.Object
    The mass and velocity of the object are defined in the presentation class, and those values are used to calculate both the momentum and kinetic energy of the object in the business logic portion of the program. This program contains the business class along with an attached javadoc file.
